                               'Permu' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Permu' is a @{"Workbench game" link play} where you try to match a pattern of
tiles shown at the upper right in the game window in the least
amount of moves.

  You can choose any game board size you like, from a 4 by 4 tiles
board, up to a 9 by 9 tiles board size.

  Have fun!

